## Key Design Decisions

### Why Next.js over Vite?

- **SSR/SSG Support** - Better for SEO and performance
- **API Routes** - Built-in backend without separate server
- **File-based Routing** - Scales better than React Router
- **Image Optimization** - Next/Image for automatic optimization
- **Production Ready** - Better developer experience for SaaS

### Why Supabase over Custom Backend?

- **Speed** - Get auth, database, storage in minutes
- **RLS** - Database-level security built-in
- **Realtime** - WebSocket support out of the box
- **Cost** - Free tier is generous for MVP
- **Migration Path** - Can self-host later if needed

### Why ShadCN UI over Material/Ant Design?

- **Notion-like Aesthetic** - Matches our design vision
- **Customizable** - Copy/paste components, full control
- **Accessible** - Built on Radix UI primitives
- **No Bundle Bloat** - Only includes what you use
- **Tailwind Native** - Consistent styling approach

### Why Zustand + React Query over Redux?

- **Simpler API** - Less boilerplate than Redux
- **Better DX** - Easier to learn and maintain
- **Separate Concerns** - Server state (RQ) vs UI state (Zustand)
- **Performance** - Minimal re-renders
- **TypeScript** - Excellent type inference

